119
00:05:52,510 --> 00:05:54,360
Although people outside all say

120
00:05:54,950 --> 00:05:56,190
she was harmed by a vengeful spirit,

121
00:05:57,160 --> 00:05:58,950
the old servants in the manor all say

122
