Then one day, for some reason,

135
00:06:31,680 --> 00:06:33,510
he burned all the paper figurines.

136
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,480
He only kept one.

137
00:06:35,480 --> 00:06:37,190
The one that most resembled Madam Yunyin.

138
