00:07:46,240 --> 00:07:46,750
Sir

159
00:07:47,040 --> 00:07:48,040
Have you found the body?

160
00:07:50,560 --> 00:07:51,950
We can't find it, and we can't look for it either.

161
00:07:52,390 --> 00:07:55,510
All the constables in Lingzhou are overwhelmed right now.

162
00:07:55,600 --> 00:07:56,510
They're too busy.

163
00:07:57,000 --> 00:07:57,600
